Authors of GNU MP MS Windows/64bit port (in chronological order of initial contribution)

Ingo A. Kubbilun	
			- conversion of all x86-64 assembler sources to ml64.exe
			  syntax
			- conversion of System V AMD64 ABI to MS Visual C/C++ AMD64
			  ABI (assembler source codes)
			- conversion of all Aarch64/ARM64 assembler sources to
			  armasm64.exe syntax
			- nmake Makefile
			- module definition files for DLLs
			- wintestrunner.c: execution and benchmarking of all tests
			- creation of DLL version resource
			- GNU MP source codes patches for MS Windows
